user_Help_reg_wh_content1: Fill in the form and click the "Submit" button
user_Help_reg_wh_content2: Warehouse ID number is given to each Warehouse and cannot be changed
user_Help_reg_wh_content3: Warehouses then have been requested registration is displayed yellow in the 'warehouse registration list'
user_Help_reg_wh_content4: Warehouses that have been rejected are displayed red in the 'Warehouse Registration List'. After checking the reason for rejection through the "View" button, click "Delete" to remove it from the list.
user_Help_reg_wh_content5: The warehouse where the administrator has approved the registration is displayed green in 'My Warehouse'
user_Help_edit_wh_content1: Click the INFO button in the warehouses you want to edit.
user_Help_edit_wh_content2: Click the "edit" button on the right of "Warehouse Info".
user_Help_edit_wh_content3: Edit the warehouse information and click the "apply" button.
user_Help_edit_wh_content4: Warehouse name and address cannot be changed.
user_Help_del_wh_content: Please contact service@autoinven.com to delete the warehouse.
user_Help_iot_content1: This service can only be applied for registered warehouses.
user_Help_iot_content2: Check the warehouse ID and name in "My Warehouse", click the "Request Service" button and check the status become "Pending Approval".
user_Help_iot_content3: Application for use of IoT service can be canceled before the administrator approves it.
user_Help_iot_content4: If the administrator approves, you can use the "IoT Page" button.
user_Help_wh_use_content1: You can check "Buy Request Info", "Warehouse Info", and "Buyer Info" in "Warehouse Buy Request List".
user_Help_wh_use_content2: Click "approved" to enter "Waiting for Payment" status. When the user completes the payment, it moves to the list of "Warehouse Usage".
user_Help_wh_use_content3: If you click "reject", a form will appear where you can enter the reason for rejection. If the reason for rejection is entered, the user can confirm it.
user_Help_check_wh_content1: You can check the current warehouse usage status by clicking the "info" button in "My Warehouse".
user_Help_check_wh_content2: In "Warehouse Usage", the warehouse that are currently being used by buyer are in green, and the ones waiting to be used are in yellow.
user_Help_check_wh_content3: Previous warehouse usage history can be checked in "Previous Warehouse Usage".
user_Help_check_wh_content4: You can check user information by using the "info" button in all usage history.
user_Help_serach_content1: You can search for warehouse in the google map.
user_Help_serach_content2: Click a warehouse and you can see the information of it.
user_Help_serach_content3: By clicking "request" button, you can fill in the form and submit.
user_Help_serach_content4: You can then check the approval state in "My Warehouse > Request Status".
user_Help_check_history_content1: You can check the current warehouse usage status by clicking the "info" button in "My Warehouse".
user_Help_check_history_content2: In "Warehouse Usage", the warehouse that are currently being used by buyer are in green, and the ones waiting to be used are in yellow
user_Help_check_history_content3: Previous warehouse usage history can be checked in "Previous Warehouse Usage".
user_Help_check_history_content4: You can check user information by using the "info" button in all usage history.
user_Help_check_req_content1: You can check your current warehouse approval state in "Request Status".
user_Help_check_req_content2: Approval can be rejected by administrator or warehouse provider, and if rejected you can click "View" for the reason.
user_Help_check_req_content3: Payment can be made after all approvals.
user_Help_pay_content1: Payment is made in two main ways: Pay via PayPal or Payment using debit card or credit card.
user_Help_pay_content2: After payment, you can check the warehouse usage in "My Warehouse > Usage Status" and access the warehouse you have payed for.
user_Help_update_user_content1: If you need update for your data, You can edit it in "MYINFO" page.
user_Help_update_user_content2: Please contact service@autoinven.com to delete the warehouse.
user_Help_forgot_content: Please enter your email address and your password will be sent to the email address registered with your account and then you can creat your new password. Or you can send e-mail via service@autoinven.com.
user_Help_area_content: Area is expressed in square meters(㎡), and prices are expressed in USD(＄).
user_Help_how_pay_content: AUTOINVEN.com Secure Payment aims to provide a safe payment service for membership. By partnering with an online payment platform (PayPal), AUTOINVEN.com provides payment security to membership.
by_findwh_searchhint: Search the location by UpSide SearchBar.
main_slogan: Connect to the Global Automotive Industry
main_p1: Provide a warehouse and earn money!
main_p2: Use the space you need for as long as you need at an affordable price!
main_p3: Check the status of the warehouse where goods are stored in real time!
